## Note on Content License

The infrastructure code (GitHub Actions, scripts, documentation) is licensed
under the MIT License above.

Individual messages submitted to the time capsule remain the intellectual 
property of their respective authors. By submitting a message, contributors 
grant permission for:

1. The message to be encrypted and stored in this repository
2. The message to be publicly revealed on January 1, 2035
3. The message to be preserved as part of this historical archive

Contributors retain all other rights to their messages.
